&lt;p&gt;I made this simple but fast paced endless 2D side scrolling platformer mobile game by myself, including the procedural art.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“Endless Mine” is a game about a miner which goes far into a procedurally generated cave to collect gems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The player is challenged by many randomized obstacles on his way and can jump with his cart to dodge them or collect additional gems to increase his score.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Play 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://ramter77.github.io/EndlessMine/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;
    Endless Mine WebGL
&lt;/a&gt;
.&lt;/p&gt;
